{"tid":721741,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"年輕人 究竟有乜野驅使你對另一半失去信任？","createTime":"2018-06-29T01:48:40.000Z","updateTime":"2018-06-29T10:59:02.000Z","uid":32176,"like":2,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"20b7a3da981b9e99ab37d0b4b07476fb3cecacd9","tid":721741,"uid":32176,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-29T01:48:40.000Z","msg":"宜段感情中 大家都十分愛對方 到宜一刻 我都仲係很愛<br />\n但一旦失去對 對方既信任...果種無力感好重 <br />\n<br />\n雖然佢冇好確實做過任何事 <br />\n但種種既行為 舉止 反應 都引發到猜疑既感覺<br />\n其實當十分著緊對方 會有胡思亂想 擔心 害怕既時候 係好唔正常？<br />\n<br />\n一心認為大家可以坦誠相對 任何事都可以講<br />\n結果 令件事 越來越嚴重 亦令到段關係好似步入結束階段咁<br />\n<br />\n我過於執著去尋根究底 原來換來既 反而係對我既不信任同佢心中既一條刺 <br />\n但種種既反應 令我更加想尋根究底 <br />\n<br />\n好忐忑 糾結"},{"pid":"29908e8530971a881a0f02a4d0e0eec4ca84c862","tid":721741,"uid":138138,"like":6,"dislike":4,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-29T01:54:42.000Z","msg":"＊▅&deg;&times;愛情就如毒癮〃還是愈早戒掉愈好`&times;[]*﹡&nbsp;"},{"pid":"eddee90e3a169592e7a71a6d558c1b9131213a20","tid":721741,"uid":75372,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-29T02:03:16.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ff9727c8bc892af0b75aeed83104a6b12a288583","tid":721741,"uid":26774,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-29T02:09:24.000Z","msg":"因為望住佢就好似以前既自己"},{"pid":"488fbc1ec649d0de679abe1793b87bc7f670f3d7","tid":721741,"uid":32176,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"ff9727c8bc892af0b75aeed83104a6b12a288583","tid":721741,"uid":26774,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-29T02:09:24.000Z","msg":"因為望住佢就好似以前既自己"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-29T02:50:57.000Z","msg":"望唔透<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"eef0e96224de62d8c50fa7f9b2c9fd0e5c511b2a","tid":721741,"uid":146637,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-29T02:52:34.000Z","msg":"係窮啊 屌你老母"},{"pid":"6d32c0766543ba170627f7b03a815ce6ad8f11d0","tid":721741,"uid":32176,"